        <hl1>Man Charged in Defacing Of Five Church Statues</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Primus St Croix is indicted on charges of vandalizing five statues at Roman Catholic churches in Brooklyn (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The Brooklyn district attorney announced the indictment yesterday of a man accused of vandalizing five statues at Roman Catholic churches in Brooklyn. The man, Primus St. Croix, 33, was charged with criminal mischief and other crimes.</p>
      </block>
